{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-{post}-tsx-content-file-path-null","path":"/2022/02-25-css-text-ellipsis/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2>한 줄의 텍스트</h2>\n<p>한 줄의 텍스트는 <code>text-overflow</code> 프로퍼티를 사용해 말줄임표 처리를 할 수 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.ellipsis-text</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">text-overflow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> ellipsis<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">overflow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> hidden<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">white-space</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> nowrap<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 360px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1px solid gray<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>ellipsis-text<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  같이, 노래하며 하였으며, 우리 황금시대의 가치를 몸이 있으랴? 그들은 청춘의\n  물방아 풀이 긴지라 인간이 생생하며, 힘차게 그리하였는가?\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>결과</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 371px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/85db089c68b4a876b9a8e70ec56a8154/d60d6/result1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 8.333333333333332%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAIAAADXZGvcAAAACXBIWXMAAA7DAAAOwwHHb6hkAAAAZ0lEQVR42g2MWw7DIAzAev/TrVUJCRDlARTQtJ5hWP6z5OP3vhgAPiflZG6plBiBC2/XGCnn6p6I7jtwEVNFDL01t0pUjjFmQmTAXdrT1f26TtuIftcSldYqYgSIJu77TjB6n89klj+/nWgktkc8rwAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/85db089c68b4a876b9a8e70ec56a8154/89b46/result1.webp 180w,\n/static/85db089c68b4a876b9a8e70ec56a8154/97ead/result1.webp 360w,\n/static/85db089c68b4a876b9a8e70ec56a8154/78533/result1.webp 371w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 371px) 100vw, 371px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/85db089c68b4a876b9a8e70ec56a8154/96042/result1.png 180w,\n/static/85db089c68b4a876b9a8e70ec56a8154/7a322/result1.png 360w,\n/static/85db089c68b4a876b9a8e70ec56a8154/d60d6/result1.png 371w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 371px) 100vw, 371px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/85db089c68b4a876b9a8e70ec56a8154/d60d6/result1.png\"\n            alt=\"result1\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><code>text-overflow</code>는 단지 텍스트가 오버플로(컨텐츠가 상자 밖으로 넘침) 상태일 때 어떻게 처리할지를 지정해주는 프로퍼티라서 혼자 있을 땐 아무런 의미가 없다. 따라서 <code>overflow</code>, <code>white-space</code> 프로퍼티를 통해 텍스트 오버플로를 발생시켜야 한다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>overflow</code>: 상자 밖으로 나간 컨텐츠를 어떻게 처리할지를 결정한다. <code>hidden</code>으로 지정하면 밖으로 튀어나온 컨텐츠를 안 보이게 만든다.</li>\n<li><code>white-space</code>: 상자 내의 화이트 스페이스(white space)를 어떻게 처리할지를 결정한다. <code>nowrap</code>으로 지정하면 공백을 축소(collapse)하고 줄바꿈하지 않게 만든다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>따라서 <code>overflow: hidden</code>, <code>white-space: nowrap</code>과 함께 <code>text-overflow: ellipsis</code>를 적용하면 텍스트는 한 줄이 되고 상자 밖으로 나가면 말줄임표 처리가 된다.</p>\n<br />\n<h2>여러 줄의 텍스트</h2>\n<p><code>-webkit-line-clamp</code> 프로퍼티를 이용해 텍스트 줄 수를 강제할 수 있다. 이 프로퍼티는 <code>display: -webkit-box</code>, <code>-webkit-box-orient: vertical</code>과 함께 사용할 경우에만 동작한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.ellipsis-text-2-line</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">text-overflow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> ellipsis<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">overflow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> hidden<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> -webkit-box<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">-webkit-line-clamp</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">-webkit-box-orient</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> vertical<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">line-height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1.5em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 3em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 360px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1px solid gray<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>ellipsis-text-2-line<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  같이, 노래하며 하였으며, 우리 황금시대의 가치를 몸이 있으랴? 그들은 청춘의\n  물방아 풀이 긴지라 인간이 생생하며, 힘차게 그리하였는가?\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>결과</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 368px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3db332c3288b75ab89c8743a8a6e41d0/7fb37/result2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 15%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAADCAIAAAAcOLh5AAAACXBIWXMAAA7DAAAOwwHHb6hkAAAAjElEQVR42g3NiRGDIBAAQPvvzowC3qFyr8okylhBaGB3ICJze9pD25bmsNPu5jHOzOJipiqisCw5ZxVDXE73w44pRAAYxs+orvf9WxFXzFetzJxSUtWyF3MXJkAoJL1BwG+tbobrXmsdYgrH4T0ohVi1tYYLImZ3CzExMQJMIfh5dZGL1OtkoU639/0DeIKeKwaZgwwAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/3db332c3288b75ab89c8743a8a6e41d0/89b46/result2.webp 180w,\n/static/3db332c3288b75ab89c8743a8a6e41d0/97ead/result2.webp 360w,\n/static/3db332c3288b75ab89c8743a8a6e41d0/09e04/result2.webp 368w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 368px) 100vw, 368px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/3db332c3288b75ab89c8743a8a6e41d0/96042/result2.png 180w,\n/static/3db332c3288b75ab89c8743a8a6e41d0/7a322/result2.png 360w,\n/static/3db332c3288b75ab89c8743a8a6e41d0/7fb37/result2.png 368w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 368px) 100vw, 368px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/3db332c3288b75ab89c8743a8a6e41d0/7fb37/result2.png\"\n            alt=\"result2\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><code>-webkit-line-clamp</code>와 <code>-webkit-box-orient</code>는 비록 많은 브라우저에서 지원한다지만 표준이 아닌 만큼 크로스 브라우징에 주의할 필요가 있다. Stack Overflow의 <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/5269713/css-ellipsis-on-second-line#answer-50566101\">이 답변</a>에서는 <code>@supports</code> 규칙을 이용해 호환성을 높이는 방법을 제시하고 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.text</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">white-space</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> nowrap<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">text-overflow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> ellipsis<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">overflow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> hidden<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@supports</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token property\">-webkit-line-clamp</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">overflow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> hidden<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">text-overflow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> ellipsis<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">white-space</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> initial<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> -webkit-box<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">-webkit-line-clamp</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">-webkit-box-orient</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> vertical<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code>-webkit-line-clamp</code> 프로퍼티를 지원한다면 두 줄로, 그렇지 않다면 한 줄로 처리될 것이다.</p>\n<p>이외에 JavaScript를 통해 말줄임표 처리를 하는 방법도 있지만, CSS로 처리할 수 있는 일은 CSS를 쓰는 게 가장 좋다고 생각하기 때문에 위 방법이 제일 낫다고 생각한다.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"CSS 텍스트 말줄임표(ellipsis) 처리","date":"2022-02-25","tags":["CSS","TIL"],"thumbnail":null},"timeToRead":1}},"pageContext":{"id":"f9887c34-b37d-51fb-a8e0-f387b291cb63"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1147043159"],"slicesMap":{}}